{"tid":821234,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建議送香港人去體驗下天災","createTime":"2018-09-16T01:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T02:46:28.000Z","uid":114824,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"927869f97dd58f4cf24bc0690532f3e15789d78f","tid":821234,"uid":114824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:08:59.000Z","msg":"連登又好，fb又好，香港人淨係識講個風無料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貼膠紙無風吹過黎就話曬時間<br />\n<br />\n天災呢樣野做足準備好過搞出人命吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺日本見識過一次震度5弱嘅地震，已經覺得香港真係好幸福.....無預警嘅地震，下一秒幾時黎真係無人知，隨時無左條命都係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n既然颱風有得提早預警，真心希望各位做足預防保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n衰啲講句，唔送班人去美國試下龍捲風，日本試下地震，佢地都唔會識驚"},{"pid":"85d864f263dd18005fcdfd6ac7f91bb92c4a83ef","tid":821234,"uid":52942,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:27:38.000Z","msg":"送天災黎香港好過啦，震平哂d膠鐵港豬噢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a59a797b520425f6bcd938d416cb97753acc10d","tid":821234,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"咁宜家個風係咪冇料到？"},{"pid":"02f7d35ea4b1d44b93354006d5e215564b10a850","tid":821234,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"7a59a797b520425f6bcd938d416cb97753acc10d","tid":821234,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"咁宜家個風係咪冇料到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:42:15.000Z","msg":"關ikea咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f042c0e43784b850db6bf4cd107bfed7d8b5a2","tid":821234,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a59a797b520425f6bcd938d416cb97753acc10d","tid":821234,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"咁宜家個